1 (3) The post-adoption contact agreement and order shall constitute a custody
2 determination, and any motion to enforce, modify, or terminate the order shall
3 be filed in the newly created civil action and is governed by G.S. 7B-909.3.
4 The Administrative Office of the Courts may adopt rules and shall develop
5 and make available appropriate forms for establishing a civil file to implement
